flowRoot.flowPara: 1. Bi-variate regression of a need satisfaction variable on energy use in a given year. The distribution of data follow a typical saturation relationship.
2. Analysis and re-estimation of social outcomes if high levels of beneficial provisioning systems prevailed in all countries. High need satisfaction would be associated with lower energy use.
3. Analysis and re-estimation of social outcomes if high values of detrimental provisioning systems prevailed in all countries. High need satisfaction would be associated with higher energy use.
